title: Higher prescription sales boost CVS results
text:
Higher prescription sales boost CVS results 4:14pm BST - 00:55
Strong sales of prescription drugs and higher prices for branded pharmaceuticals drove revenue higher at CVS. As Fred Katayama reports, the new tax law helped lift the drug store chain's profit. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
